ntainer"><div class=3D"article-content-container"><div class=3D"cc"><div cl=
ass=3D"no-margin"><p>We do not allow Google-served ads on screens:</p>

<ul>
  <li>without publisher-content or with <a class=3D"glossary-term" data-ans=
wer=3D"11036238" href=3D"https://support.google.com/publisherpolicies/table=
/10563033#low-value-content" data-stats-ve=3D"40">low-value content</a>,</l=
i>
  <li>that are under construction,</li>
  <li>that are used for alerts, navigation or other behavioral purposes</li=
>
</ul>
</div>

