svg+xml"> at the bottom of the video player, then select <strong>Subtitles/=
CC</strong> and choose your language.</p>

<hr></div>

    <div>The content you provide should be of value to the user and be the =
focal point for users visiting your site or app. For this reason, we may li=
mit or disable ad serving on pages with low value content and/or still bein=
g constructed until changes are made.</div>

    <div>Additional examples that can help you understand inventory value p=
olicy:</div>

    <ul>
      <li>Ads should not be placed on "dead end" or no content screens (e.g=
., Thank You, Log in, Exit, Error pages, etc.)</li>
      <li>Ads should not be placed within apps where the sole focus of the =
interaction is the user looking away from the screen. For example, a flashl=
ight app.&nbsp;</li>
      <li>Don=E2=80=99t place ads on <a href=3D"https://support.google.com/=
webmasters/answer/2721306" rel=3D"noopener" target=3D"_blank">automatically=
 generated content</a> without manual review or curation.&nbsp;</li>
    </ul>

